      "height": 161.0,
      "z_value": -9.940000000000033,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "* **NTFS**: A widely used filesystem on Windows systems.\n* **HFS**: A filesystem used on Mac systems.\n* **ext3**: A filesystem used on Linux systems.\n* **FAT**: A simple filesystem used on older systems."
    },
