      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 116.0,
      "z_value": -9.953000000000026,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "There are several ways to manage filesystems, including:"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Omnious",
      "uuid": "55831b8fd261495ea18467b7183ffbd5",
      "x": 7524.794023805198,
      "y": 5925.791045870549,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 206.0,
      "z_value": -9.952000000000027,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "* **Creating new directories**: Using the `mkdir` command or the File Explorer.\n* **Deleting files and directories**: Using the `rm` command or the File Explorer.\n* **Copying files and directories**: Using the `cp` command or the File Explorer.\n* **Moving files and directories**: Using the `mv` command or the File Explorer."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Growth",
      "uuid": "7702a4508fa545a58c8ab871419f3678",
      "x": 7623.470027363888,
      "y": 5502.284279896423,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 116.0,
      "z_value": -9.950000000000028,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Here are some best practices for managing filesystems:"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Becoming Yours",
      "uuid": "155e56450279469ca9bca3ccd72a98ed",
      "x": 7417.124101173802,
      "y": 5162.169429229265,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 236.0,
      "z_value": -9.949000000000028,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "* **Backup your data**: Regularly backing up your files and directories is essential for ensuring the security and integrity of your data.\n* **Use compression**: Compressing files can help reduce storage space and improve transfer times.\n* **Use encryption**: Encrypting files can help protect them from unauthorized access.\n* **Use secure passwords**: Using secure passwords can help protect your files and directories from unauthorized access."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Bloom",
