      "body_text": "I hope this helps you get started with FLM! If you have any specific questions or need further guidance, feel free to ask.\n[FLM]  Model RAW Output:\nFLM (Filmora) is a popular video editing software that's known for its user-friendly interface and advanced features. Here's an overview to help you get started:"
