      "uuid": "cd169d38ca00464c8edc6f6c85edab30",
      "x": 24184.884877364395,
      "y": 6198.632959549643,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 191.0,
      "z_value": -9.863000000000076,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "As Nova continued its exploration, it eventually came across the GPU (Graphics Processing Unit). The NPU was amazed by the GPU's ability to render complex graphics, to make the laptop's systems run faster and more efficiently. It watched in awe as the system administrators executed complex tasks, their fingers flying across the keyboard with precision."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Accurate",
      "uuid": "0b41cf2028f74f99a7607123550e6f66",
      "x": 23802.62897685193,
      "y": 6261.309394655767,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 101.0,
      "z_value": -9.864000000000075,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "**Chapter 6: The GPU**"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Inner Peace",
      "uuid": "8d3e238689ba46b7b6c03fa3c979e1d9",
      "x": 24052.238379628696,
      "y": 5974.679936862183,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 176.0,
      "z_value": -9.862000000000076,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Nova learned about the various types of GPUs, from the NVIDIA GeForce to the AMD Radeon. It even attempted to execute a few commands on the GPU, but its attempts were met with failure. Undeterred, Nova continued its exploration, determined to unlock the secrets of the GPU."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Becoming Yours",
      "uuid": "8b4b525db1f64690a2e6d84527faea06",
      "x": 24721.462609290225,
      "y": 5256.130123810163,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 176.0,
      "z_value": -9.85700000000008,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "As Nova continued its exploration, it eventually came across the laptop's motherboard. The NPU was amazed by the motherboard's complexity, its intricate web of wires and circuits. It watched in awe as the system administrators executed complex tasks, their fingers flying across the keyboard with precision."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
