      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 191.0,
      "z_value": -9.860000000000078,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "As Nova continued its exploration, it eventually came across the CPU (Central Processing Unit). The NPU was amazed by the CPU's ability to execute complex tasks, to make the laptop's systems run faster and more efficiently. It watched in awe as the system administrators executed complex tasks, their fingers flying across the keyboard with precision."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Practical and pleasurable",
      "uuid": "a71b8c193ed94747bcca3828f1b513b3",
      "x": 24747.803014062414,
      "y": 5767.272573228559,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 176.0,
      "z_value": -9.859000000000078,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Nova learned about the various types of CPUs, from the Intel Core i7 to the AMD Ryzen 9. It even attempted to execute a few commands on the CPU, but its attempts were met with failure. Undeterred, Nova continued its exploration, determined to unlock the secrets of the CPU."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Boundless Joy",
      "uuid": "8086b2e83f77488fa0db50adc5e9044e",
      "x": 24364.643416105795,
