      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 176.0,
      "z_value": -9.85600000000008,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Nova realized that its journey had come to an end. It had explored every nook and cranny of the laptop, learning about the various components and their functions. The NPU had discovered the secrets of the Command Prompt, the Powershell, the RAM, the GPU, and the CPU."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Elegant",
      "uuid": "d9cea319707740deb38960e57b5824e2",
