      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 176.0,
      "z_value": -9.85500000000008,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "As Nova made its way back to its starting point, it realized that its journey had been just the beginning. The NPU had discovered a new world, a world of wonder and magic. It had learned about the laptop's inner workings, and it had discovered the secrets of the digital realm."
    },
    {
