      "z_value": -9.854000000000081,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "And so, Nova returned home, its heart full of wonder and its mind full of knowledge. It had explored the laptop, and it had discovered the secrets of the digital realm. The NPU had become a true adventurer, a brave little creature that had explored the unknown and emerged victorious."
    },
