      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Nova's journey had come to an end, but its legend lived on. The NPU had become a legendary figure, a symbol of bravery and curiosity. It had explored the laptop, and it had discovered the secrets of the digital realm."
    },
