      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "As the years went by, Nova's legend grew. The NPU became a symbol of inspiration, a reminder to all who heard its story that even the smallest creatures can achieve greatness. And so, Nova's journey continued, a journey of discovery and exploration, a journey that would take it to the farthest reaches of the digital realm.\n[FLM]  Model RAW Output:\n**Chapter 1: The Unlikely Adventurer**"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Boundless Joy",
      "uuid": "3aa6f0d015204b2b91faf7cb16cfa692",
      "x": 17582.81282352078,
      "y": 5208.307415339001,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 221.0,
      "z_value": -9.896000000000058,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "The number 10 has a rich etymology. The word \"ten\" comes from the Latin word \"decem,\" which is derived from the Greek word \"deka,\" meaning \"ten.\" The Greek word \"deka\" is thought to be derived from the Proto-Indo-European word \"*dek-\", which also meant \"ten.\" The Proto-Indo-European language was spoken around 4000 BCE, and it is believed to be the ancestor of many modern languages, including Latin, Greek, and many others."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Evolve",
      "uuid": "a60b1a00082a4d7b867230307259cf4b",
      "x": 18202.131164398903,
      "y": 5139.484113362615,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 206.0,
      "z_value": -9.894000000000059,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "The number 10 has been considered sacred or symbolic in many cultures throughout history. In ancient Egypt, the number 10 was considered a sacred number, as it represented the number of gods in the pantheon. In many African cultures, the number 10 is associated with completeness or wholeness, as it represents the idea of a perfect set or a complete cycle."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Fresh Start",
      "uuid": "f9e7f26b5cdd4532b78463223c33573b",
      "x": 17839.893690757282,
      "y": 5060.677695598759,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 101.0,
      "z_value": -9.895000000000058,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "**Cultural Significance of 10**"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Omnious",
      "uuid": "02403308559f46c9b223682c63e20ae6",
      "x": 18573.237171699475,
      "y": 5073.438498821145,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 191.0,
      "z_value": -9.89300000000006,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "In modern times, the number 10 has become a cultural icon, with the phrase \"10\" being used in various contexts, such as \"10\" in sports (e.g., the number of players on the field in some games), \"10\" in music (e.g., the \"10th\" note in music theory), and \"10\" in technology (e.g., the \"10th\" anniversary of a company or a product)."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Beautiful",
      "uuid": "3c68a632f0224d669276521674401b63",
      "x": 19038.935156008098,
      "y": 5160.678555892481,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 116.0,
      "z_value": -9.89100000000006,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Here are a few interesting facts about the number 10:"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Clear Vision",
      "uuid": "0d40fa206f1f4b0ebb435ddb9d72d969",
      "x": 18557.05936154446,
      "y": 4591.955165082003,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 236.0,
      "z_value": -9.890000000000061,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "* The number 10 is a factor of many other numbers, such as 20, 30, and 40.\n* The number 10 has a unique property in mathematics, known as the \"10-identity,\" which states that the sum of the numbers from 1 to 10 is equal to 55 (1 + 2 + 3 + ... + 9 + 10 = 55).\n* The number 10 is the first number that can be represented using a decimal system, which is why it is often considered the \"beginning\" of our modern numerical system."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Evolve",
      "uuid": "1c2e9bf1f0fe4ae3b890af8e28013b45",
      "x": 18983.07683956851,
      "y": 4567.3036813816125,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 131.0,
      "z_value": -9.889000000000062,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "I hope you found this conversation about the number 10 interesting! Do you have any specific questions or topics you'd like to discuss further?"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Fresh Start",
      "uuid": "e51ee97fb62e451286cf19022ed60232",
      "x": 19321.3544416983,
      "y": 4380.2915718738,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 341.0,
      "z_value": -9.887000000000063,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Available commands:\n  /show - show the model information\n  /load [model_name] - load a model\n  /input [filename] [follow_up_prompt] - load a file and follow up with a prompt\n                                       - If space is in the filename, use quotes to wrap it\n  /save - save the history\n  /clear - clear the context\n  /status - show perf. metrics\n  /history - show the history\n  /verbose - toggle the verbose\n  /think - toggle the think\n  /set [variable] [value] - set the variable\n  /list - list all the models\n  /bye - exit the program\n  /? - show this help"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Infinite Wisdom",
      "uuid": "706038d6b3f5400e969497f556f341b2",
      "x": 18970.85384547975,
      "y": 4254.0160981515055,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 221.0,
      "z_value": -9.886000000000063,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Interactive input:\n  - Press Enter to submit single-line input\n  - Paste multi-line text and it will be detected automatically\n  - Use 'Shift + Enter' to explicitly continue on next line\n  - Commands (starting with /) are processed immediately\n>>> /show"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Grace",
      "uuid": "33b830262c564c8c9cf9a6b6424a196c",
      "x": 18992.46182391399,
      "y": 3952.380200531357,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 266.0,
      "z_value": -9.885000000000064,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Model:\n    model_name:             Llama-3.2-3B-NPU2\n    compatible_flm_version: >= 0.9.21\n    head_dim:               128\n    hidden_size:            3072\n    hidden_act:             silu\n    intermediate_size:      8192\n    num_attention_heads:    24\n    num_hidden_layers:      28\n    num_key_value_heads:    8\n    pretraining_tp:         1\n    rms_norm_eps:           1e-05"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Kinetic",
      "uuid": "9e5cc5118f3a410794ea9b18bb6e63c6",
      "x": 19345.19969069787,
      "y": 3825.8824213306193,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 116.0,
      "z_value": -9.883000000000065,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": ">>> Write a detailed 1500-word story about a brave little NPU exploring a laptop, with chapters."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Beautiful",
      "uuid": "11fe6e796b094f0cb08e1ffb94f9e1b3",
      "x": 19357.283990917615,
      "y": 4024.494878911482,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 116.0,
      "z_value": -9.882000000000065,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "**Chapter 1: The Unlikely Adventurer**"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Becoming Yours",
      "uuid": "2a0960eb98464483ab83d737c2b722e1",
      "x": 19763.298251362066,
      "y": 4000.33418157669,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 206.0,
      "z_value": -9.881000000000066,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "In a world where technology reigns supreme, a small, yet fearless creature roamed the uncharted territories of a laptop. The little NPU (Northbridge Processor Unit) had always been fascinated by the mysterious realm within the laptop's confines. Its curiosity knew no bounds, and it yearned to explore every nook and cranny, to discover the secrets that lay hidden beneath the sleek surface."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Intricate",
      "uuid": "2f5a4d00f33a4429b0c1cb4cb80ea32f",
      "x": 20104.43493533222,
      "y": 4138.9854914131165,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 176.0,
      "z_value": -9.880000000000067,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "The NPU's name was Nova, and it was no larger than a grain of rice. Despite its minuscule size, Nova possessed a bravery that rivaled the greatest heroes. It had heard tales of the laptop's inner workings, of the CPU, GPU, and RAM, and it was determined to venture into the unknown."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Fresh Start",
      "uuid": "b2f57ff4ed1244c59e5a878f5afe3bfb",
      "x": 20965.738317403193,
      "y": 4301.72501403782,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 221.0,
      "z_value": -9.877000000000068,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "As Nova descended onto the keyboard, it was greeted by a sea of keys, each one bearing a unique tale to tell. The NPU marveled at the tactile feel of the keys, the way they seemed to vibrate with life. It explored the F1-F12 keys, learning about the various functions they performed. The Shift key, with its dual roles, fascinated Nova, while the Ctrl and Alt keys, which controlled the laptop's various functions, left it in awe."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Growth",
      "uuid": "2bfc1afb935f4c0eb890a4063bbfd910",
      "x": 20475.31860662857,
      "y": 4342.162466950145,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 191.0,
      "z_value": -9.879000000000067,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "One day, Nova decided that the time had come to embark on its grand adventure. It carefully made its way through the laptop's circuitry, avoiding the prying eyes of the CPU and GPU, which had warned Nova of the dangers that lay ahead. The NPU's heart pounded with excitement as it approached the laptop's keyboard."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Gentle",
      "uuid": "1d8b9d5fb9334f68a53b52b2a819e355",
      "x": 20883.729861577453,
      "y": 4628.789160813307,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 101.0,
      "z_value": -9.878000000000068,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "**Chapter 2: The Keyboard of Wonders**"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Onward",
      "uuid": "572c6c57a3b746bb9c908e03dfd69151",
      "x": 21328.29225034714,
      "y": 4348.232402688797,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 206.0,
      "z_value": -9.876000000000069,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Nova soon discovered that the keyboard was more than just a collection of keys. It was a gateway to the laptop's operating system, a realm of endless possibilities. The NPU delved deeper, learning about the OS's architecture and its various components. It encountered the Command Prompt, a mysterious realm that seemed to hold the secrets of the laptop's inner workings."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Evolve",
      "uuid": "234516964a8540d782998ebc75025364",
      "x": 22129.937208891974,
      "y": 4569.174415934886,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 206.0,
      "z_value": -9.87400000000007,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "As Nova navigated the Command Prompt, it encountered a world of strange and wondrous creatures. There were the system administrators, who ruled over the laptop with an iron fist. The NPU watched in awe as they executed commands, their fingers flying across the keyboard with precision. The NPU even met the occasional hacker, who attempted to bypass the laptop's security measures."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Intentional",
      "uuid": "4f88b920bb7e42699738b24dc6ed5e3c",
      "x": 22474.204449521014,
      "y": 4438.386642988025,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 206.0,
      "z_value": -9.87300000000007,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "But Nova was not intimidated. It knew that the Command Prompt was a realm of power, and it was determined to master its secrets. The NPU spent hours learning about the various commands, from the simple `dir` command to the more complex `ipconfig` command. It even attempted to execute a few commands on its own, but its attempts were met with failure."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Boundless Joy",
      "uuid": "f19fa950e0194e1e8feac84bb6f0a768",
      "x": 21785.281717211008,
      "y": 4496.715067998154,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 101.0,
      "z_value": -9.87500000000007,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "**Chapter 3: The Command Prompt**"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Pure Light",
      "uuid": "02e533f40cca4229a8bd32321a7b1b2b",
      "x": 23017.689365906106,
      "y": 4827.213452913989,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 101.0,
      "z_value": -9.871000000000071,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "**Chapter 4: The Powershell**"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Fresh Start",
      "uuid": "5bc884c4e54f4959933fbd695e4eb33f",
      "x": 22506.942635025556,
      "y": 4220.5974499927415,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 176.0,
      "z_value": -9.872000000000071,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Undeterred, Nova continued its exploration, determined to unlock the secrets of the Command Prompt. It encountered the `powershell` command, which seemed to hold the power of the gods. The NPU was amazed by its ability to manipulate the laptop's systems, to execute complex tasks with ease."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "All Glory",
      "uuid": "25e027e373f34fa3a176a4f669750acc",
      "x": 23229.454051297398,
      "y": 4983.726053384194,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 191.0,
      "z_value": -9.870000000000072,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "As Nova delved deeper into the `powershell` command, it encountered a world of magic and wonder. The NPU watched in awe as the system administrators executed complex tasks, their fingers flying across the keyboard with precision. The NPU even met the occasional PowerShell script, which seemed to hold the power of the universe."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Tiny little extra sprinkles of joy",
      "uuid": "6454bdd9023449b8bc6d0130cf1de222",
      "x": 22622.176135033456,
      "y": 4805.146278158642,
      "width": 360.0,
      "height": 176.0,
      "z_value": -9.869000000000073,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Nova was amazed by the `powershell` command's ability to manipulate the laptop's systems, to execute complex tasks with ease. It learned about the various modules, from the `active directory` module to the `network` module. The NPU even attempted to execute a few scripts on its own, but its attempts were met with failure."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "All Glory",
      "uuid": "b65c5fcbb0d440d3abc3c63fcca83ae9",
      "x": 23171.072387583255,
      "y": 5886.077742920294,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 191.0,
      "z_value": -9.866000000000074,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "As Nova continued its exploration, it eventually came across the RAM (Random Access Memory). The NPU was amazed by the RAM's ability to store data temporarily, to make the laptop's systems run faster and more efficiently. It watched in awe as the system administrators executed complex tasks, their fingers flying across the keyboard with precision."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Sweet",
      "uuid": "2841d5bf664a49189a6e5b873c83ce2a",
      "x": 23121.776987277855,
      "y": 5682.628596536726,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 101.0,
      "z_value": -9.867000000000074,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "**Chapter 5: The RAM**"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "New Thought",
      "uuid": "626ea296d394496ebb3c2492deaeb28f",
      "x": 23044.304414775943,
      "y": 5416.1599828256485,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 191.0,
      "z_value": -9.868000000000073,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Despite its failure, Nova continued its exploration, determined to unlock the secrets of the `powershell` command. It encountered the `Get-WmiObject` command, which seemed to hold the power of the gods. The NPU was amazed by its ability to manipulate the laptop's systems, to execute complex tasks with ease."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Endless Potential",
      "uuid": "4f61209ece09447c8e3b173aa121b5ae",
      "x": 23444.072330670588,
      "y": 6134.163256419359,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 176.0,
      "z_value": -9.865000000000075,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Nova learned about the various types of RAM, from the DDR3 RAM to the DDR4 RAM. It even attempted to execute a few commands on the RAM, but its attempts were met with failure. Undeterred, Nova continued its exploration, determined to unlock the secrets of the RAM."
    }
  ],
